EFUN: capitalize

SYNTAX:
string capitalize( str );
  string str;

DESCRIPTION:
This converts the first character in 'str' to upper case.

RETURN VALUE:
The modified string is returned.

SEE ALSO:
upper_case
lower_case

EXAMPLE:
string mud_name;

mud_name = capitalize( "holy mission" );
// mud_name is now "Holy mission".

